Articles.Content:
These Pictures were snapped during the first ever expedition to the mountain range near the Kerbal Space Centre early on during KSP's history, the Biplane, a Kleport K-14 FK1 (First-Kerbal-War) fighter, converted to a science craft, went missing, a few decades later, 2 pictures where recovered, amongst the wreckage of the biplane, the rest were located around KSC's buildings.. It is thought Bilman was trying to land and crashed into a rise in the terrain, wrecking the FK1 era biplane beyond repair. He has never been found. (pictures modified using the "Movie Time" mod.)
